channel.title: Else If Error - Chat Filter Help
channel.description:
Okay, so I made a post not to long ago, and got alot of the errors fixed, but Now I have one... It says:
[code]src\server\Connection.java:313: 'else' without 'if' else /\ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code] I put else if where the else is and i get more errors. Help!

item.title: Else If Error - Chat Filter Help
item.dc:creator: @shank_beast shank beast
item.description:
@shank_beast wrote:

the “else” needs brackets, try this

} else {

Or

} else if

Read full topic
